OL,3,CCouple fear losing life savings after
OL,4,Cinvesting in bankrupt company
OL,6,FA couple from North Wales fear they've
OL,7,Flost more than #400,000 of their life
OL,8,Fsavings, after investing in an asset
OL,9,Fmanagement company.
OL,11,FThe 79th Group based in Southport sold
OL,12,Floan notes to investors, supposedly
OL,13,Fsecured against property, including in
OL,14,Freal estate, and investments in
OL,15,Fnatural resources.
OL,17,FBut in April this year, the company
OL,18,Fwent into administration, leaving
OL,19,Fthousands of investors without their
OL,20,Fmoney.
