OL,3,CCouple fear losing life savings after
OL,4,Cinvesting in bankrupt company
OL,6,FSpeaking on Y Byd ar Bedwar, S4C's
OL,7,FCurrent Affairs Programme, Angharad
OL,8,Fand Alun, not their real names, said
OL,9,Fthe situation has left them in a "very
OL,10,Fdark place."
OL,12,F"It has made us sick. We have been
OL,13,Fleft in a desperate situation. Our
OL,14,Flives have been affected in such a way
OL,15,Fthat I can never forgive the business
OL,16,Ffor what they've done to us," said
OL,17,FAngharad.
OL,19,FThe 79th Group said it was an asset
OL,20,Fmanagement company that offered high
OL,21,Finterest rates for investors.
