OL,3,CCouple fear losing life savings after
OL,4,Cinvesting in bankrupt company
OL,6,FAlun said that they started investing
OL,7,Fabout 10 years ago.
OL,9,F"It started with small investments,
OL,10,F#5,000 to #10,000 at a time. As you
OL,11,Finvested more and more, the rate of
OL,12,Finterest improved. Maybe 12%, and then
OL,13,Fthe rate of interest increases."
OL,15,FThe 79th group is the same company
OL,16,Fthat bought Penrhos Park on Anglesey
OL,17,Fto develop a 250 million pound holiday
OL,18,Fresort on the site.
