OL,3,CCouple fear losing life savings after
OL,4,Cinvesting in bankrupt company
OL,6,F"It seemed to work well, and the more
OL,7,Fmoney that came in we were then able
OL,8,Fto invest more. This in turn meant we
OL,9,Fcould retire," says Angharad.
OL,11,FIn February, the City of London police
OL,12,Flaunched an investigation for
OL,13,Fwidespread fraud and arrested four
OL,14,Fpeople associated with the company.
OL,16,FBy April, The 79th Group had gone into
OL,17,Fadministration.
OL,19,FBy this point, Angharad and Alun say
OL,20,Fthey had #430,000 in their account.
