OL,3,CCouple fear losing life savings after
OL,4,Cinvesting in bankrupt company
OL,6,FThey say they haven't seen any of that
OL,7,Fmoney since the 79th Group went under.
OL,9,F"It really hurts. It's likely that we
OL,10,Fwill have to go back to work at the
OL,11,Fexact time you hope you will be able
OL,12,Fto retire."
OL,14,F3,700 other investors also trusted
OL,15,Fthis company and many have been left
OL,16,Fdevastated when the payments stopped
OL,17,Fat the start of this year.
