OL,3,CCouple fear losing life savings after
OL,4,Cinvesting in bankrupt company
OL,6,FEmma, not her real name, from South
OL,7,FWales, decided to invest #50,000 of
OL,8,Fher savings in November last year. She
OL,9,Fclaims she was told that she would
OL,10,Freceive #3,750 twice a year, with 15%
OL,11,Finterest on the original investment.
OL,13,FEmma says she never received the
OL,14,Finterest and has not seen any sign of
OL,15,Fthe #50,000 that she invested either.
OL,17,F"I depended on the money. We have to
OL,18,Fcut down on food, electricity,
OL,19,Fheating, petrol, travel, the holidays
OL,20,Fwe go on. Rethink everything.
