OL,6,F"It's hard to describe how I feel -
OL,7,Fnumb maybe."
OL,9,FThe City of London police says its
OL,10,Finvestigation is ongoing and they are
OL,11,Fworking through a substantial volume
OL,12,Fof material. They say their priority
OL,13,Fis to support victims throughout the
OL,14,Fprocess.
OL,16,FY Byd ar Bedwar has contacted the
OL,17,Fdirectors of the 79th Group, David
OL,18,FWebster, Curtis Webster and Jake
OL,19,FWebster but have not received a
OL,20,Fresponse.
